creator: DiversyFund
descriptionHtml:
DiversyFund opens up a brand new category of investing to the everyday investor: private alternative assets. Diversifying your portfolio has never been easier. Open your account, make your first investment, and instantly become a co-owner of a diversified portfolio with the click of a button.

DiversyFund is breaking down barriers to alternative assets by opening up high-value investments without the typical high cost of entry. Its first open fund, the DF Growth REIT, offers investors a chance to participate in a once unattainable asset class, multifamily real estate, starting with just a $500 minimum investment.

Historically, alternative investments like real estate have outperformed traditional stocks and bonds. During market uncertainty, multifamily properties (cash flowing apartment buildings) specifically tend to be much less or not affected by an economic downturn. It’s time to make your portfolio stronger and invest for your future. Download the application and start investing today!

“Best for investors looking for a low-cost entry into real estate investing.” - Nerdwallet (1)

+POWERED BY TECHNOLOGY - Using the app, you can easily track how your investment portfolio grows, including property updates, reports, market research, and progress through the REIT cycle.
.
+ SUPERCHARGE IRA DOLLARS - Put your retirement dollars to work instead of leaving them in a low-growth, traditional retirement account. You can even use your IRA to open your DiversyFund account.

+ DIVERSIFY AWAY - We make it easy to diversify away from stocks and bonds and into real estate - with historically higher returns and less market volatility. With DiversyFund, we make balancing your portfolio as simple as a tap on your screen..

+ GROW YOUR KNOWLEDGE - Custom real estate and investing content to grow your financial literacy & demystify real estate investing, right in your app.

RESPONSIBLE & SMART REAL ESTATE INVESTING

INVESTING PHILOSOPHY: We believe that real estate is the most powerful way to create & maintain wealth. We make it easy to diversify beyond stocks and bonds, so you can access commercial real estate deals. With DiversyFund, you can tap into an investing strategy that the uber-wealthy use and invest in your own future.

BACKED BY THE BEST: DiversyFund REITs are managed by in-house real estate experts with 40+ years of experience helping investors just like you. Our experts are here every step of the way to help grow your money & get the highest potential return.

HANDS-OFF INVESTING: Download the app and discover the easiest way to balance your investment portfolio and diversify. Set your goals and risk tolerance, and we’ll take care of the rest.
